EPL - Match of the Day 3rd & 4th Nov 2018 720p HD
Video : MKV; H.264; 1280x720; 50 fps, ~3000 kbps
Audio : English (AC3, 6ch, 384 Kbps, 48 kHz)
03.11.2018: Gary Lineker presents highlights from Saturday's Premier League matches, which included Arsenal's clash with Liverpool. Elsewhere, Manchester United travelled to the south coast for a tricky-looking fixture against a Bournemouth side that have started the season superbly. Tottenham also faced a difficult test away at Wolves, who have begun life back in the Premier League with aplomb.

04.11.2018: Highlights from the day's Premier League games, including champions Manchester City taking on Southampton.

Also playing were Chelsea, who have made an impressive start to the season under new manager Maurizio Sarri. They take on Crystal Palace at Stamford Bridge.

Presenter Mark Chapman also brings you all the goals and talking points from Saturday's matches
